question.title: "Cannot resolve com.squareup.okhttp3:mockwebserver:unknown" error after upgrade to Spring Boot 3.4.0
question.body:
After upgrade to Spring Boot 3.4.0 from 3.3.x, I get an error

Cannot resolve com.squareup.okhttp3:mockwebserver:unknown

My project uses okhttp3.mockwebserver.MockWebServer and has the dependency

<dependency>
    <groupId>com.squareup.okhttp3</groupId>
    <artifactId>mockwebserver</artifactId>
    <scope>test</scope>
</dependency>

I have not changed anything else but the Spring Boot version, and everything has worked OK until now.
